31#include <stdio.h>
32#include "gmp.h"
33#include "gmp-impl.h"
34
35
36/* mpn_divexact_by3 was a function in gmp 3.0.1, but as of gmp 3.1 it's a
37 macro calling mpn_divexact_by3c. */
38mp_limb_t
39__MPN (divexact_by3) (mp_ptr dst, mp_srcptr src, mp_size_t size)
40{
41 return mpn_divexact_by3 (dst, src, size);
42}
43
44
45/* mpn_divmod_1 was a function in gmp 3.0.1 and earlier, but marked obsolete
46 in both gmp 2 and 3. As of gmp 3.1 it's a macro calling mpn_divrem_1. */
47mp_limb_t
48__MPN (divmod_1) (mp_ptr dst, mp_srcptr src, mp_size_t size, mp_limb_t divisor)
49{
50 return mpn_divmod_1 (dst, src, size, divisor);
51}
52
53
54/* mpz_legendre was a separate function in gmp 3.1.1 and earlier, but as of
55 4.0 it's a #define alias for mpz_jacobi. */
56int
57__gmpz_legendre (mpz_srcptr a, mpz_srcptr b)
58{
59 return mpz_jacobi (a, b);
60}
